text: Now that's a rocking GameBoy tune by Alberto Gonzalez like few other composers could do. It's incredible that the tiny portable machine could produce a sound like that. GameFAQs and this screenshot shows a 1993 release date, but Wikipedia and Giantbomb say 1990. If anyone can confirm, let me know! Also, I'll now try to add the composers' YouTube channel in the description if they have one, so check it out! If I ever forget to add a channel in the description, let me know.
